# View 1 – Department with Highest Attrition (Last 2 Years)

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW VW_ATTRITION_BY_DEPARTMENT AS
SELECT
    d.DEPARTMENT_NAME,
    COUNT(fa.ATTRITION_ID) AS TOTAL_ATTRITIONS
FROM FACT_ATTRITION fa
JOIN DIM_DEPARTMENT d
    ON fa.DEPT_SK = d.DEPT_SK
JOIN DIM_CALENDER c
    ON fa.DAY_SK = c.DAY_SK
WHERE c.FULL_DATE >= ADD_MONTHS(SYSDATE, -24)
GROUP BY d.DEPARTMENT_NAME;
```

### To View the Result

```sql
SELECT *
FROM VW_ATTRITION_BY_DEPARTMENT
ORDER BY TOTAL_ATTRITIONS DESC;
```

