# View 2 – Average Performance Rating by Exit Type

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW VW_PERFORMANCE_EXIT_ANALYSIS AS
SELECT
    fa.EXIT_REASON_CATEGORY,
    ROUND(AVG(fp.RATING_SCORE),2) AS AVERAGE_RATING
FROM FACT_ATTRITION fa
JOIN FACT_PERFORMANCE fp
    ON fa.EMP_SK = fp.EMP_SK
WHERE fa.EXIT_REASON_CATEGORY IN ('Voluntary','Involuntary')
GROUP BY fa.EXIT_REASON_CATEGORY;
```

### To View the Result

```sql
SELECT *
FROM VW_PERFORMANCE_EXIT_ANALYSIS;
```

