# View 3 – Replacement Cost by Business Unit

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW VW_REPLACEMENT_COST AS
SELECT
    d.BUSINESS_UNIT,
    SUM(fa.ESTIMATED_REPLACEMENT_COST) AS TOTAL_REPLACEMENT_COST
FROM FACT_ATTRITION fa
JOIN DIM_DEPARTMENT d
    ON fa.DEPT_SK = d.DEPT_SK
JOIN DIM_CALENDER c
    ON fa.DAY_SK = c.DAY_SK
WHERE c.YEAR = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM ADD_MONTHS(SYSDATE,-12))
GROUP BY d.BUSINESS_UNIT;
```

### To View the Result

```sql
SELECT *
FROM VW_REPLACEMENT_COST
ORDER BY TOTAL_REPLACEMENT_COST DESC;
```

