# View 4 – Promotion vs Attrition Within 12 Months

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW VW_PROMOTION_ATTRITION AS
SELECT
    ROUND(
        COUNT(DISTINCT fa.EMP_SK) * 100 /
        COUNT(DISTINCT fp.EMP_SK),
        2
    ) AS ATTRITION_RATE_PERCENT
FROM FACT_PERFORMANCE fp
LEFT JOIN FACT_ATTRITION fa
       ON fp.EMP_SK = fa.EMP_SK
      AND fa.DAY_SK BETWEEN fp.DAY_SK
                        AND fp.DAY_SK + 365
WHERE fp.PROMOTION_FLAG = 'Y';
```

### To View the Result

```sql
SELECT *
FROM VW_PROMOTION_ATTRITION;
```

